lwanga (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Full compiler with LLVM backend
  * Support for x86_64 and ARM64 architectures
  * Inline assembly support (Intel and AT&T syntax)
  * Direct syscall interface
  * Position-independent code generation
  * Encrypted string literals
  * Code formatter (lwangafmt) with logo headers
  * Syntax highlighter (lwangacat) with multiple themes
  * Comprehensive test suite (20+ tests)
  * Example programs included
  * File type icons and MIME type registration

